OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHalifax joins rivals in    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcutting mortgage rates     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Halifax is set to sharply cut rates on 
OL,6, some of its fixed mortgage deals,      
OL,7, potentially easing pressure on some    
OL,8, homeowners.                            
OL,10,FThe UK's biggest mortgage lender will  
OL,11,Freduce rates by up to 0.71 percentage  
OL,12,Fpoints from Friday, with a five-year   
OL,13,Ffixed deal priced at 5.39% from 6.10%. 
OL,15,FOther lenders such as HSBC, Nationwide 
OL,16,Fand TSB have cut some rates.           
OL,18,FMortgage costs have risen as the Bank  
OL,19,Fof England has pushed up interest rates
OL,20,Fin a bid to tame soaring prices.       
